        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", with intentional solemnity (Weiss, Weizsäcker). The words are sometimes taken to mean that Paul simply encourages them by his own example to eat. But Blass, see critical note, who comments “et oratione confirmat et exemplo,” adds in [419] text ",
        "children": []
